comment: Turner (IND) and Jennings (ORL) make incidental contact with one another while jumping for the loose ball.
George (IND) makes contact with Gordon (ORL) after he secures the rebound.
Mahinmi (IND) sets the hand-off screen on Oladipo (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Vucevic (ORL) maintains legal guarding position on Ellis's (IND) drive, placing a bent forearm to his side as he drives below the free-throw line and not affecting his RSBQ.
L-SLA shows that Fournier (ORL) cleanly strips the ball from George (IND).
Mahinmi (IND) sets the screen on Oladipo (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Mahinmi (IND) sets the screen on Fournier (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Mahinmi (IND) makes incidental contact with Vucevic (ORL) after he secures the inbounds pass.
Turner's (IND) left arm makes contact with Vucevic's (ORL) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Although Oladipo (ORL) draws Ellis (IND) into the air on his jump shot attempt, there would have been no contact if Oladipo hadn't jumped sideways into Ellis.
Gordon (ORL) commits a take foul on Turner (IND).
